[X] All lists and tasks are rendered on load/reload

[X] Lists are displayed out in columns across the page

[X] Lists can be Created

[X] Lists and tasks each have a delete button

[X] List creation must include a title limited to 3-15 characters

[X] List creation must include a color picker or minimum 5 different colors

[] Lists include a count of all tasks compared to uncompleted tasks

[X] Each List must have its own Task form

[] Task title/body must be between 3-50 characters

[] Tasks can be marked complete, this will persist on reload

[X] Forms should not submit unless the fields adhere to the requirements

[X] Lists can be Deleted

[X] Tasks can be Deleted (seperate from being marked complete)

[] Users are prompted to confirm any delete (search window.confirm)